<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/661086-does-anyone-know-why-the-book-is-called">Does anyone know why the book is called Sad Cypress?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_661086'><a id="like_count_community_question_661086" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/661086?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">3 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F433035.Sad_Cypress">like</a></span>

