<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/11938133-osenka"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_100x100-259587f1619f5253426a4fa6fb508831.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/11938133-osenka">Osenka</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">This comes from wikipedia :<br/><br/>The title comes from a song from Act II, Scene IV of Shakespeare&apos;s Twelfth Night which is printed as an epigraph to the nov<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">This comes from wikipedia :<br /><br />The title comes from a song from Act II, Scene IV of Shakespeare's Twelfth Night which is printed as an epigraph to the novel.<br /><br />Come away, come away, death,<br />And in sad cypress let me be laid;<br />Fly away, fly away breath;<br />I am slain by a fair cruel maid.<br />My shroud of white, stuck all with yew,<br />O, prepare it!<br />My part of death, no one so true<br />Did share it.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
