<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1192843-i-couldn-t-make-the-connection-between-the">I couldn&#39;t make the connection between the title and the story. Answers here do not really provide clarity. Can anyone else offer an opinion as to why the book is called Sad Cypress?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1192843'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F433035.Sad_Cypress">like</a></span>

</li>
