<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I think it is the line, &quot;I&apos;ve been slain by a fair cruel maid,&quot; in the quote from Shakespeare.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I think it is the line, "I've been slain by a fair cruel maid," in the quote from Shakespeare.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
