      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/2019627-sad-cypress">Quotes from Sad Cypress</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Ah, but life is like that! It does not permit you to arrange and order it as you will. It will not permit you to escape emotion, to live by the intellect and by reason! You cannot say, 'I will feel so much and no more.' Life, Mr. Welman, whatever else it is, is not reasonable. [Hercule Poirot]&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/quotes/471094-ah-but-life-is-like-that-it-does-not-permit">77 likes</a>
            </nobr>
            <div class="clear"></div>
